name: Figma55 Source Files
description:
Hey there!


You've found the new continually updated resource for all of the videos from "Figma55", a project by Brendan Miller of Cloud City Development where I cover Figma tips/tricks and plugins in under one minute.


If you've found this file and haven't watched the series, you can find it here:

https://www.youtube.com/c/figma55


And you can find twitter updates about figma55 here:

https://twitter.com/figma55
